doc: Models missing from Users & Permissions Application dropdown
**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**

I've created a few models using the Content Type Builder. After creating new models and going to the Users & Permissions / Application dropdown, I'm unable to see the new models in this area. This happens on the hosted version. Locally, I'm able to see the new models.
**If the current behavior is a bug, please provide the steps to reproduce the problem**
The models will be missing to select actions. They are visible on the left handle panel, but not within this menu.
Can select actions on any new items created via Content Type Builder
